objects.query: SELECT CurrencyIsoCode, Description, Id, Name FROM FulfillmentWorkspace
SELECT CurrencyIsoCode, Id, Name, UsageType FROM FulfillmentStepDefinitionGroup
SELECT CurrencyIsoCode, ErrorCode, FlowDefinitionName, Id, IntegrationDefinition.DeveloperName, Name, RetriesAllowed, RetryIntervals, RetryPolicy, StepType FROM FulfillmentFalloutRule

SELECT CurrencyIsoCode, EstimatedDuration, EstimatedDurationUnit, FlowDefinition, Id, StepType, JeopardyThreshold, JeopardyThresholdUnit, Name, IntegrationDefinition.DeveloperName FROM FulfillmentStepJeopardyRule

SELECT CurrencyIsoCode, AssignedToId, ExecuteOnRuleId, FlowDefinitionName, Id, IntegrationDefinitionNameId, Name, OmniscriptName, ResumeOnRuleId, RunAsUserId, Scope, StepDefinitionGroupId, StepType, UsageType FROM FulfillmentStepDefinition
SELECT CurrencyIsoCode, DependencyScope, DependsOnStepDefinitionId, FulfillmentStepDefinitionId, Id, Name FROM FulfillmentStepDependencyDef
SELECT CurrencyIsoCode, FulfillmentStepDefinitionGroupId, FulfillmentWorkspaceId, Id, ShowOrder FROM FulfillmentWorkspaceItem

SELECT CurrencyIsoCode, DestinationProductId, Id, Name, Priority, SourceProductId FROM ProductFulfillmentDecompRule ORDER BY SourceProduct.StockKeepingUnit ASC, DestinationProduct.StockKeepingUnit ASC
SELECT CurrencyIsoCode, Action, FulfillmentStepDefnGroupId, Id, Name, ProductId  FROM ProductFulfillmentScenario
SELECT DecompositionScope, FulfillmentQtyCalcMethod, Name, StockKeepingUnit FROM Product2 ORDER BY Product2.StockKeepingUnit ASC
